---
name: Retro 80s Synthwave
description: Style preset — Retro 80s Synthwave
tags: [style, retro, aspect-16:9]
---
Render as a retro 1980s synthwave-styled diagram on a dark purple-to-black gradient background. Use hot pink, electric cyan, and neon yellow for lines, shapes, and text. Add subtle scan-line effects and a retro grid perspective floor fading into the background. Use a bold, blocky retro font for all labels. The result should feel like a tech diagram from an 80s sci-fi movie -- glowing, vibrant, and unmistakably retro-futuristic.
